item.title: Prayer bpn13033 in Kube
item.description: Kewu uŋwambuŋga baecsêc, amaiguc, ama qeru qutulaŋ amaiguc, ic embac qeri iguc, zuŋ boŋŋaiguc baec sasaŋgia iguc, baŋec iguc, tumuya iguc baecsêc iguc, kênduŋ iguc. Baec komoc iguc, tomoc baec iguc, zêma baec dimia Kewu mepêsimu. Imi Kewu sêcgêma kecdaczac. (Source category: Uŋwambuŋga Baecsêc) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13033)
